<h2>1. Project Directives: From Concept to Execution</h2>

<h3>1.1 The Strategic Objective</h3>
<p>The "Lightweight Learning Tracker" project was initiated to solve a critical operational bottleneck: <strong>How do we upskill a 10-person engineering squad without incurring the 20% overhead of a traditional LMS?</strong></p>
<p>The solution, <strong>SkillVector</strong>, is not just a "tracker". It is a <strong>High-Velocity Competency Engine</strong> designed to:</p>
<ol>
    <li><strong>Reduce Admin Latency:</strong> Managers should spend < 5 seconds per week checking compliance.</li>
    <li><strong>Enforce Active Learning:</strong> Passive watching is blocked via "Heartbeat Telemetry".</li>
    <li><strong>Preserve Context:</strong> Learning notes are cryptographically bound to video timestamps.</li>
</ol>

<h3>1.2 User Psychology & Personas</h3>

<h4>üß† The Learner: "Flow-State Sarah" (Senior Engineer)</h4>
<ul>
    <li><strong>The Problem:</strong> Training tools usually break focus. Finding a specific note from a 2-hour video is impossible.</li>
    <li><strong>The Solution (UX):</strong> <strong>Contextual Memory.</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Feature - Deep-Link Note Taking:</strong> When Sarah types a note at <code>14:02</code>, clicking that note later instantly seeks the video to <code>14:02</code>.</li>
</ul>

<h4>üëÆ The Admin: "Governance Mike" (Director)</h4>
<ul>
    <li><strong>The Problem:</strong> "I don't trust self-reported progress."</li>
    <li><strong>The Solution (Architecture):</strong> <strong>Trustless Verification.</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Feature - The Green Board:</strong> A traffic-light dashboard showing instant compliance status.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. Architectural Decision Records (The "How")</h2>

<h3>2.1 The Tech Stack: "Velocity vs. Robustness"</h3>
<p>We architected the system using the <strong>SupaStack (Supabase + React)</strong> pattern.</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Frontend (The Head):</strong> <strong>React + Vite on Edge CDN.</strong> Instant load times (&lt;100ms).</li>
    <li><strong>Backend (The Muscle):</strong> <strong>Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth).</strong> ACID transaction guarantees to satisfy compliance auditing.</li>
</ul>

<h3>2.2 Critical Logic: The "Smart Watchdog"</h3>
<p>To prevent "Cheat-Skipping":</p>
<ol>
    <li><strong>Heartbeat Protocol:</strong> Client emits a cryptographic pulse every 30 seconds.</li>
    <li><strong>Server Validation:</strong> <code>IF (NewTimestamp - LastTimestamp > 40s) THEN REJECT</code>.</li>
</ol>

