<h2>5. Deployment & Production Strategy</h2>
<h3>5.1 Continuous Integration (CI/CD)</h3>
<p>We utilize a <strong>GitOps</strong> workflow to ensure stability.</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Source:</strong> <code>git push origin main</code>.</li>
    <li><strong>Deploy:</strong> Vercel (Frontend) + Supabase CLI (DB Migrations).</li>
</ul>

<h3>5.2 Security Posture (Zero Trust)</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Identity:</strong> No "Superuser" keys in the client. All access is Token-Based (JWT).</li>
    <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> All streams TLS 1.3 encrypted.</li>
</ul>

